::KitKat::


She realized that they may detect her soon if they scanned for bots in the 
area.  She followed her instincts.  She quietly left her hiding place and 
crept away.  She finally got out of scanner range and ran through the trees 
and back to the Pred base.  She walked through the entrance.  She saw 
Quickstrike sitting at DarkMouse's console.  She walked over to him and 
transformed into bot mode. She leaned against the console and looked at 
Quickstrike. "What's the matter? You look frusterated. Anything I can do to 
help?"
